class  QuadcopterGui
 The Gui Class which sends commands to OnboardNodeHandler through GuiCommandMessages. It shows the states of various modes using check boxes and has buttons for commands without states. The Gui Class updates the checkboxes based on user inputs and also based on inputs from OnboardNodeHandler. More...
